rows.label: tev074201_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: tev074201_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Nen'celeg about Noctilum.

rows.label: tev074201_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss

rows.label: tev074201_SEL1021
rows.name: Ask Nen'celeg about recent developments.

rows.label: tev074201_SEL0031
rows.name: Ask Nen'celeg about Noctilum.

rows.label: tev074201_MSG0001
rows.name:
Noctilum is rife with dangerous indigens.
It is certainly not a safe place to visit.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev074201_MSG0002
rows.name:
Nevertheless, I find my trips there to be calming.
You might say that for us Orphe,
it puts our Ovah at ease.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev074201_MSG0003
rows.name:
When I visited there recently, I discovered Absop's
swallowtails at a place called Rust Lake.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev074201_MSG0004
rows.name:
I couldn't stop watching them. At the moment of their
deaths, they emit the most radiant light. It's incredible.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev074201_MSG0005
rows.name:
I want to do more research. I suspect there may be
some connection between that place and the origins of
we Orphe.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev074201_MSG0013
rows.name: Thank you for rescuing me in Noctilum.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev074201_MSG0014
rows.name:
You need not worry about me any longer.
Having found a promising subject for my research,
I do not intend to leave New LA again for some time.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev074201_MSG0015
rows.name:
You are curious about my research subject?
Well, it is none other than Nan'celeg.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev074201_MSG0016
rows.name:
He seems to have some interest in me,
yet does not seem to understand the fundamental
reasoning behind that interest.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev074201_MSG0017
rows.name:
We Orphe are more interesting than any indigen.
I intend to use Nan'celeg as a test subject in
researching the way we Orphe think.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev074201_MSG0025
rows.name:
There is a place at the heart of Noctilum that sets my
Ovah aflutter.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev074201_MSG0026
rows.name:
I know there is something there.
Something other than indigens and the Ganglion.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev074201_MSG0027
rows.name:
I would love to perform a more thorough study,
but Nan'celeg will not permit it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev074201_MSG0028
rows.name:
I could ignore his objections, but I have no desire to
worry him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev074201_MSG0029
rows.name:
Every day I scour FrontierNav for information as I fight
back the urge to run off there myself.[ST:wait ]
